3
00:00:19,670 --> 00:00:21,610
Prosecutor Kim.

4
00:00:23,150 --> 00:00:26,400
Are you sure you have proof?

5
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:28,510
I want to ask you.

6
00:00:28,510 --> 00:00:31,690
For someone who knows psychopaths so well,

7
00:00:33,240 --> 00:00:36,470
how did you not recognize the one right next to you?

8
00:01:08,650 --> 00:01:14,320
The Yellow Umbrella killer was... your fiancée.

9
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:17,660
How could you end up with that kind of a woman?

10
00:01:59,540 --> 00:02:03,710
Ms. Baek Sang Ah, do you acknowledge

11
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:07,750
murdering Im Hwa Yeong on March 10th, 2020?

12
00:02:21,610 --> 00:02:25,650
Attempted murder of Detective Joo and killing and abandoning Kim Hee Soo,

13
00:02:25,650 --> 00:02:28,930
killing Gang Do Cheol, do you acknowledge all of them?

14
00:02:28,930 --> 00:02:30,020
Soo Hyeok.

15
00:02:30,020 --> 00:02:34,680
I asked if you acknowledge them, Ms. Baek Sang Ah.

16
00:02:42,580 --> 00:02:45,020
Did you really kill them?

17
00:02:45,020 --> 00:02:45,830
I don't know.

18
00:02:45,830 --> 00:02:50,720
You've been killing people while I was with you?

19
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:54,770
You knew how much I hate animals like that.

20
00:02:56,950 --> 00:03:00,780
Why? Why did you kill them?

21
00:03:03,830 --> 00:03:05,620
Tell me.

22
00:03:06,950 --> 00:03:09,310
Do you know something?

23
00:03:09,310 --> 00:03:14,860
At this moment, all your attention is on me.

24
00:03:15,710 --> 00:03:22,340
What kind of person am I? Did I really kill people?

25
00:03:22,340 --> 00:03:25,590
You're sincerely curious about me.

26
00:03:25,590 --> 00:03:27,120
What?

27
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:32,290
I'm going to tell you one by one very slowly.

28
00:03:32,290 --> 00:03:35,520
Only you, Prosecutor Kim.

29
00:03:37,480 --> 00:03:43,170
That way, I can see you here like this for a long time.

30
00:03:46,930 --> 00:03:50,090
What is your relationship to Gong In Woo?

31
00:03:50,090 --> 00:03:52,310
Who is he?

32
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:57,090
You're so curious about me.

33
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:00,450
I like it.

34
00:04:22,370 --> 00:04:25,990
In Do, there's a scratch on her wrist.

35
00:04:25,990 --> 00:04:27,480
Check under the nails of the victim.

36
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:30,710
Pardon? Yes.

37
00:04:51,010 --> 00:04:54,070
     

38
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:12,200
It's me. The remains of the convict, make sure it's resolved as unidentifiable.

39
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:14,670
Make sure it can't be reconstructed.

40
00:05:20,970 --> 00:05:23,350
Chief Prosecutor, Ms. Jang Hye Mi is here.

41
00:05:23,350 --> 00:05:25,280
You may let her in.

42
00:05:47,310 --> 00:05:49,660
Did you come because of your daughter?

43
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:54,020
It's not so surprising such a child was born in your family.

44
00:05:54,020 --> 00:05:57,770
What could she have learned from a mother who protects a murderer?

45
00:05:57,770 --> 00:06:03,820
That's the reason I broke up with you 30 years ago.

46
00:06:03,820 --> 00:06:06,170
Lack of morals.

47
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:09,410
I'll give you five minutes.

48
00:06:10,290 --> 00:06:12,500
Gong Ji Cheol came back alive.

49
00:06:12,500 --> 00:06:14,490
Gong Ji Cheol?

50
00:06:15,240 --> 00:06:18,220
Right. He did, not too long ago.

51
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:19,960
He's lying in the autopsy room as we speak.

52
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:22,750
I've already fixed it so that he's unidentifiable and cannot be reconstructed.

53
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:26,150
Did you come here because you were scared about it?

54
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:38,640
What you really need to be scared about is the case from 30 years ago,

55
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:45,990
the Yellow Umbrella killer. The fact that Gong Ji Cheol isn't the real culprit.

56
00:06:45,990 --> 00:06:51,950
And... you and I conspiring together and killing Gong Ji Cheol...

57
00:06:51,950 --> 00:06:54,570
You haven't forgotten, have you?

58
00:06:57,400 --> 00:06:59,230
So?

59
00:06:59,230 --> 00:07:00,520
Let Sang Ah go.

60
00:07:00,520 --> 00:07:02,370
She's committed murder.

61
00:07:02,370 --> 00:07:05,350
So did you 30 years ago.

62
00:07:05,350 --> 00:07:07,560
- What? 
 - Let my daughter go.

63
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:09,460
